---
import DefaultLayout from "../../../../layouts/default.astro";
---

<DefaultLayout>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20 lg:py-24">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">
        Last updated: October 24, 2025
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none text-gray-600">
      <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        <strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">De Het</strong> ("the App") is developed and maintained by <strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pavel Yuruts</strong> ("we," "us," or "our"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our mobile application available on Android and iOS platforms.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-gray-200" />

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          We value your privacy and aim to collect only the minimum data necessary to provide and improve the App's functionality. The App does not require account creation or registration. You can use all features of the App without providing your name, email address, phone number, or any other personally identifiable information.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1.1. Analytics Data</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              We use third-party analytics tools, such as <strong class="font-medium text-gray-900">Firebase Analytics</strong> and <strong class="font-medium text-gray-900">Google Analytics for Firebase</strong>, to understand how users interact with the App. These services automatically collect anonymous information such as:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 marker:text-gray-400">
              <li>App usage data (e.g., screens visited, features used)</li>
              <li>Device information (e.g., model, OS version)</li>
              <li>Approximate location (country or region)</li>
              <li>Interaction duration and frequency</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">
              This information helps us improve performance, usability, and user experience.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1.2. Crash Logs</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              We use <strong class="font-medium text-gray-900">Firebase Crashlytics</strong> to detect and analyze unexpected errors or app crashes. This includes non-personal technical data, such as:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 marker:text-gray-400">
              <li>Stack traces</li>
              <li>Device model and OS version</li>
              <li>App version</li>
              <li>Timestamps of crashes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1.3. Device Identifiers</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We may collect device identifiers (e.g., Firebase Instance ID) to enable essential app services such as notifications or analytics tracking. These identifiers are anonymized and not linked to personally identifiable information.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1.4. Local Storage</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              The App uses <strong class="font-medium text-gray-900">SharedPreferences</strong> (local storage) to save data directly on your device, such as:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 marker:text-gray-400">
              <li>User preferences</li>
              <li>Usage counters</li>
              <li>Offline progress or settings</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">
              This information never leaves your device and is not transmitted to external servers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="my-12 border-gray-200" />

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">2. How We Use the Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">We use collected data for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 marker:text-gray-400 mb-6">
          <li>To analyze app performance and improve stability</li>
          <li>To enhance and personalize user experience</li>
          <li>To understand usage trends and identify potential improvements</li>
          <li>To fix crashes and bugs efficiently</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          We are committed to an ad-free experience. We do not display third-party advertisements, and we do not sell, rent, or trade your data to any third parties using the App.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="my-12 border-gray-200" />

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">3. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Our App is intended for users of all ages, including children.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          We do not knowingly collect or request any personally identifiable information from children under 13 years of age. All analytics and crash data collected are anonymous and used solely to maintain the App's performance and safety.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="my-12 border-gray-200" />

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          We take reasonable steps to protect all collected information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. Data transmitted to third-party analytics providers is encrypted and handled in accordance with their respective privacy policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="my-12 border-gray-200" />

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-4">
          <li>
            <strong class="block font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Google Firebase (Analytics, Crashlytics)</strong>
            <a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 group w-fit">
              Firebase Privacy Policy
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 opacity-0 -ml-2 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:ml-0 transition-all">
                 <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 10a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h6.638L10.23 7.29a.75.75 0 111.04-1.08l3.5 3.25a.75.75 0 010 1.08l-3.5 3.25a.75.75 0 11-1.04-1.08l2.158-1.96H5.75A.75.75 0 015 10z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="block font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Google Play Services</strong>
            <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 group w-fit">
              Google Privacy Policy
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 opacity-0 -ml-2 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:ml-0 transition-all">
                 <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 10a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h6.638L10.23 7.29a.75.75 0 111.04-1.08l3.5 3.25a.75.75 0 010 1.08l-3.5 3.25a.75.75 0 11-1.04-1.08l2.158-1.96H5.75A.75.75 0 015 10z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
          These services comply with GDPR, CCPA, and COPPA requirements.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="my-12 border-gray-200" />

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">6. Data Retention and Control</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Since we do not collect personal identifiers, we cannot retrieve, export, or delete historical data associated with a specific individual upon request.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 marker:text-gray-400">
          <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> You can stop all collection of information by the App easily by uninstalling the App.</li>
          <li><strong>Retention:</strong> Anonymous analytics data is retained in our systems for a limited period (typically up to 14 months) to allow for year-over-year analysis, after which it is automatically deleted or aggregated.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <hr class="my-12 border-gray-200" />

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be reflected in this document with a new "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this page from time to time to stay informed about how we protect your data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="my-12 border-gray-200" />

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          If you have any questions, concerns, or requests about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8">
           <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
             <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
               <span class="text-2xl">ðŸ“§</span>
               <div>
                  <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 mb-1">Email</div>
                  <a href="mailto:pavel.yuruts@gmail.com" class="text-gray-900 font-medium hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">pavel.yuruts@gmail.com</a>
               </div>
             </div>
             <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
               <span class="text-2xl">ðŸ‘¤</span>
               <div>
                  <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 mb-1">Developer</div>
                  <div class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Pavel Yuruts</div>
               </div>
             </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</DefaultLayout>
